author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Bathroom exhaust fan insulation tips…I have an exhaust vent for the bathroom fan. But there’s a gap between it and the plywood. I’m using Great Stuff Wide Spray to fill that gap. This reduces the likelihood of air leaks and condensation that can cause mold or mildew.
